  • Deprecated Classes 
    Class and Description
    org.apache.iceberg.parquet.ParquetWriteAdapter
    use ParquetWriter
  • Deprecated Exceptions 
    Exceptions and Description
    org.apache.iceberg.exceptions.RuntimeIOException
    Use java.io.UncheckedIOException directly instead. Exception used to wrap IOException as a RuntimeException and add context.
  • Deprecated Fields 
    Field and Description
    org.apache.iceberg.mr.InputFormatConfig.CATALOG
    please use InputFormatConfig.catalogPropertyConfigKey(String, String) with config key CatalogUtil.ICEBERG_CATALOG_TYPE to specify the type of a catalog.
    org.apache.iceberg.mr.InputFormatConfig.CATALOG_LOADER_CLASS
    please use InputFormatConfig.catalogPropertyConfigKey(String, String) with config key CatalogProperties.CATALOG_IMPL to specify the implementation of a catalog.
    org.apache.iceberg.mr.InputFormatConfig.HADOOP_CATALOG_WAREHOUSE_LOCATION
    please use InputFormatConfig.catalogPropertyConfigKey(String, String) with config key CatalogProperties.WAREHOUSE_LOCATION to specify the warehouse location of a catalog.
    org.apache.iceberg.TableProperties.MERGE_CARDINALITY_CHECK_ENABLED
    will be removed in 0.14.0, the cardinality check is always performed starting from 0.13.0.
    org.apache.iceberg.TableProperties.MERGE_CARDINALITY_CHECK_ENABLED_DEFAULT
    will be removed in 0.14.0, the cardinality check is always performed starting from 0.13.0.
    org.apache.iceberg.TableProperties.OBJECT_STORE_PATH
    Use TableProperties.WRITE_DATA_LOCATION instead.
    org.apache.spark.sql.catalyst.parser.extensions.IcebergSqlExtensionsParser.tokenNames
    Use IcebergSqlExtensionsParser.VOCABULARY instead.
    org.apache.spark.sql.catalyst.parser.extensions.IcebergSqlExtensionsLexer.tokenNames
    Use IcebergSqlExtensionsLexer.VOCABULARY instead.
    org.apache.iceberg.TableProperties.WRITE_DISTRIBUTION_MODE_DEFAULT
    will be removed in 0.14.0, use specific modes instead
    org.apache.iceberg.TableProperties.WRITE_FOLDER_STORAGE_LOCATION
    Use TableProperties.WRITE_DATA_LOCATION instead.
    org.apache.iceberg.TableProperties.WRITE_NEW_DATA_LOCATION
    will be removed in 0.14.0, use TableProperties.WRITE_DATA_LOCATION instead
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    org.apache.iceberg.io.DataWriter.add(T)
    since 0.13.0, will be removed in 0.14.0; use DataWriter.write(Object) instead.
    org.apache.iceberg.flink.sink.FlinkSink.Builder.build()
    this will be removed in 0.14.0; use FlinkSink.Builder.append() because its returned DataStreamSink has a more correct data type.
    org.apache.iceberg.orc.ORC.WriteBuilder.config(String, String)
    Please use #set(String, String) instead
    org.apache.iceberg.deletes.PositionDeleteWriter.delete(CharSequence, long)
    since 0.13.0, will be removed in 0.14.0; use PositionDeleteWriter.write(PositionDelete) instead.
    org.apache.iceberg.deletes.PositionDeleteWriter.delete(CharSequence, long, T)
    since 0.13.0, will be removed in 0.14.0; use PositionDeleteWriter.write(PositionDelete) instead.
    org.apache.iceberg.deletes.EqualityDeleteWriter.delete(T)
    since 0.13.0, will be removed in 0.14.0; use EqualityDeleteWriter.write(Object) instead.
    org.apache.iceberg.deletes.EqualityDeleteWriter.deleteAll(Iterable<T>)
    since 0.13.0, will be removed in 0.14.0; use FileWriter.write(Iterable) instead.
    org.apache.iceberg.MetricsConfig.fromProperties(Map<String, String>)
    use MetricsConfig.forTable(Table)
    org.apache.spark.sql.catalyst.parser.extensions.IcebergSqlExtensionsParser.getTokenNames()
    org.apache.spark.sql.catalyst.parser.extensions.IcebergSqlExtensionsLexer.getTokenNames()
    org.apache.iceberg.spark.SparkTableUtil.listPartition(SparkTableUtil.SparkPartition, PartitionSpec, SerializableConfiguration, MetricsConfig)
    use TableMigrationUtil.listPartition(Map, String, String, PartitionSpec, Configuration, MetricsConfig, NameMapping)
    org.apache.iceberg.spark.SparkTableUtil.listPartition(SparkTableUtil.SparkPartition, PartitionSpec, SerializableConfiguration, MetricsConfig, NameMapping)
    use TableMigrationUtil.listPartition(Map, String, String, PartitionSpec, Configuration, MetricsConfig, NameMapping)
    org.apache.iceberg.Table.rollback()
    Replaced by Table.manageSnapshots()
    org.apache.iceberg.Rollback.toSnapshotAtTime(long)
    Replaced by ManageSnapshots.rollbackToTime(long)
    org.apache.iceberg.Rollback.toSnapshotId(long)
    Replaced by ManageSnapshots.setCurrentSnapshot(long)
    org.apache.iceberg.RowDelta.validateNoConflictingAppends(Expression)
    since 0.13.0, will be removed in 0.14.0; use RowDelta.conflictDetectionFilter(Expression) and RowDelta.validateNoConflictingDataFiles() instead.
    org.apache.iceberg.OverwriteFiles.validateNoConflictingAppends(Expression)
    since 0.13.0, will be removed in 0.14.0; use OverwriteFiles.conflictDetectionFilter(Expression) and OverwriteFiles.validateNoConflictingData() instead.
